# Base URL for em-solar-api (no trailing slash). Used by Vite dev `runtime-config.js` and optional build-time embed.
#
# Local `vite dev`: unset or `http://localhost:8787` — dev server probes `/health` on :8787; if down,
# `/runtime-config.js` uses the live API URL from `src/config/api-default-url.ts`. Set VITE_API_URL
# to a full https URL to skip probing and force that API.
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8787
#
# --- Cloudflare Worker (this repo) — live API URL ---------------------------
# Deployed **em-solar** Worker: plaintext **API_BASE_URL**. `/runtime-config.js` sets
# `window.__EM_SOLAR_API_BASE__` to that URL so the browser calls the backend origin directly.
#
# Optional: bake URL into the static JS at build time (CI): VITE_API_URL=https://your-api.workers.dev
